skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to daily updates from UK Fundraising, for news, ideas and opportunities for charity and nonprofit fundraisers. 

You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing", or "Alexa, play fundraising news". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
